text: Ruben Josefson (25 August 1907, Svenljunga, Sweden - 19 March 1972, Uppsala, Sweden) was a Swedish bishop. He was active within the Church of Sweden. He was the Archbishop of Uppsala between 1967 and 1972. == References == Category:1907 births Category:1972 deaths Category:Swedish clergy Category:Archbishops of Uppsala
